Description:
Complimentary 3-month Adobe Creative Cloud subscription with the purchase. Learn more on ASUS website for more details
ASUS VivoBook Pro 15 OLED laptop comes with 15.6” FHD (1920 x 1080) 16:9 aspect ratio with ultra-slim NanoEdge bezels
The laptop comes with 144Hz refresh rate, 100% sRGB color gamut, Pantone Validated and TÜV Rheinland-certified
Latest Intel Core i7-12650H Processor 2.3 GHz (24M Cache, up to 4.7 GHz, 6P cores + 4E cores)
NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3050 Laptop GPU, with 64GB GDDR6 - Studio Ready
Fast storage and memory featuring 512GB M.2 NVMe PCIe 3.0 SSD and 16GB DDR4 on board RAM, Windows 11 Home
Extensive connectivity with Thunderbolt 4, USB-C 3.2 Gen2 (display/power), USB-A 3.2, 3.5mm Combo Jack, Micro SD card reader, HDMI 2.0a, RJ45 Gigabit Ethernet, Wi-Fi 6E (802.11ax) and Bluetooth 5 (*USB transfer speed may vary. Learn more at ASUS.com)
